gs=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Introduction<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab621bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ab621bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In today&#8217;s rapidly changing insurance climate, having the right tools available to manage their workload, retrieve customer data, and monitor progress in deals and cases keeps agents competitive. To deliver better service and keep up with the customers who tend to respond quickly, insurance companies have to provide their salespersons with the necessary technology so that workflows are optimized. They know everything about customer needs upfront when providing agents with the tools and information they need to do their job, and a solid agent portal can serve as the command center for access to task completion and enablement in dealing with customers.<\/p><p>Modern agents are anything but a luxury\u2014they&#8217;re becoming necessary for agents and carriers alike who want greater efficiencies and better outcomes. We dig deeper into why it is crucial for insurance companies today to create a feature-rich agent portal and how embedding it with the CRM can turn your agents around.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c511a7 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1c511a7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-2\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The Role of an Agent Portal in Modern Insurance<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f61826 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7f61826\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>At its core, an agent portal is a gateway between insurance agents and the internal systems that store customer and policy information. Rather than having agents sift through various disconnected platforms to find the needed data, an agent portal consolidates this information into one easy-to-navigate dashboard. This portal should integrate seamlessly with the company\u2019s <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/crm-implementation-enhancements\/\">CRM<\/a> to give agents a full view of the customer lifecycle, including active policies, pending claims, and open cases.<\/p><p>For agents, time is money. The less time they spend on admin tasks, the more time they have to create relationships and ultimately close business. A well-designed agent portal enables agents to log in and see all their cases and all the deals they are tracking so that instead of maintaining a diary, they can simply go through deal-by-deal and complete it.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d9c4845 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d9c4845\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-3\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Key Features of a Robust Agent Portal<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05e35a6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"05e35a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>To deliver real value, an agent portal must include several critical features designed to enhance usability, provide up-to-date insights, and ensure a streamlined workflow.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b5c4d8d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b5c4d8d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">1. CRM Integration for Real-Time Data<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-447c63d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"447c63d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The backbone of any effective agent portal is its integration with the company\u2019s CRM system. This connection lets the portal pull real-time data about cases, deals, and customer interactions. For example, when <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/salesforce\/\">Salesforce<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/hubspot\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HubSpot<\/a> are integrated, agents can see where the customer is in their sales funnel\u2014not only what policies they have bought in the past but also any recent insurance claims. Agents need this kind of visibility to prepare to bring the most current and relevant information with them every time they engage their customers.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6f0da20 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6f0da20\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2. Centralized Case and Deal Management<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d414e57 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d414e57\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A robust portal allows agents to see all their open cases and deals in one view. Agents can access everything they need in a single location rather than logging into multiple systems or manually tracking progress through spreadsheets. With this setting, agents can check which policies need to be renewed, find out which cases require follow-up, and track submission or approval deadlines. It&#8217;s all about creating a seamless user experience that reduces friction and optimizes workflow.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2d1d253 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2d1d253\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">3. Automated Notifications and Alerts<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-26ebc5c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"26ebc5c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Keeping track of deadlines and milestones is for sure a challenging thing. And when agents manage multiple clients simultaneously, it does become a headache. To address this, agent portals should provide automated notifications for critical events. Just simple as agents receiving monthly or daily reminders when cases approach important milestones. This ensures that nothing slips through the cracks and helps agents stay proactive in managing their book of business.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-35ea97a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"35ea97a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">4. Detailed Analytics and Insights<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1bd795 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f1bd795\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Accessibility is a literal non-negotiable in today&#8217;s mobile-first business universe. Agents should be able to access the portal from their mobile devices to manage their workload. The ability to check deal status, answer questions, or submit documents from anywhere helps ensure that agents remain productive no matter where they are.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32f1edc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"32f1edc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">5. Mobile Accessibility<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5b9e2cf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5b9e2cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In today\u2019s mobile-first world, accessibility is non-negotiable. Agents should be able to access the portal from their mobile devices to manage their workload on the go. Whether they\u2019re at a client meeting or working remotely, the ability to check the status of deals, respond to inquiries, or submit documents from anywhere ensures that agents remain productive regardless of location.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1bdc6f6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1bdc6f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/mobile-devices-to-manage-their-workload-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17006\" alt=\"mobile devices to manage their workload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/mobile-devices-to-manage-their-workload-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/mobile-devices-to-manage-their-workload-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/mobile-devices-to-manage-their-workload-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/mobile-devices-to-manage-their-workload.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-74cf866 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"74cf866\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-4\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Insurance Companies Need a Modern Agent Portal<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-559a4a5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"559a4a5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The insurance industry is known for its complexity. Agents often deal with various products, regulations, and customer needs. Creating a robust agent portal makes these processes more manageable. It allows agents to focus on delivering value to customers rather than navigating clunky systems.<\/p><p>Here\u2019s why a modern agent portal is a must-have for today\u2019s insurance companies:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3cdad31 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3cdad31\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">1. Increased Efficiency<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25ef5a9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"25ef5a9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A centralized agent portal reduces the time agents spend searching for information or switching between platforms. By keeping everything in one place, Agents can be more productive and handle more cases, which ultimately increases their earning potential.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f967961 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f967961\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2. Improved Customer Service<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-900436f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"900436f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Access to real-time data and information allows agents to anticipate customer needs. Whether processing a claim or renewing a policy, Portals help ensure agents stay ahead of the curve. This leads to better customer service and greater customer satisfaction.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8eb012c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8eb012c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">3. Better Decision-Making with Data<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-442ca21 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"442ca21\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Analytics tools within the portal help agents make data-driven decisions. Whether understanding which customers are ready to buy or any cases requiring immediate action, access to these insights helps agents prioritize their workloads more efficiently.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1df6d70 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1df6d70\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Data-driven-decisions-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16935\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Data-driven-decisions-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Data-driven-decisions-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Data-driven-decisions-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Data-driven-decisions-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Data-driven-decisions.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e6f5e83 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e6f5e83\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">4. Enhanced Collaboration<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-40833af elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"40833af\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>An agent portal can facilitate better collaboration across departments for larger insurance teams. When everyone on the team has acess to all the information, everyone is aligned the right way when working a client\u2019s case.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb2701e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bb2701e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">5. Scalability<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-02992b6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"02992b6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>As your business grows, the number of agents and clients you need to manage will grow as well. A strong portal should grow with you, offering flexibility, new features, integrations, and users as your needs evolve.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ad5300d all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ad5300d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-5\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Final Thoughts: A Portal for the Future of Insurance<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d17c9f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6d17c9f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In the insurance world, having the rightly built agent portal is more than just about making things smoother. It\u2019s about giving your agents the right tools to serve the clients better. Seamless CRM integration, automated notifications, and detailed insights, that is one recipe to get your agent portal in order.<\/p><p>At <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mountainise<\/a>, we believe technology is the key to helping your agents reach their full potential. If you&#8217;re serious about improving operations and boosting agent performance, building a future-ready portal should be at the top of your list.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-354b991\" data-id=\"354b991\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-f6c1df6 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f6c1df6\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;],&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-dc958e3\" data-id=\"dc958e3\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c08b47d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c08b47d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Latest WhitePaper<\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-07a3f03 elementor-grid-1 elementor-grid-tablet-2 elementor-grid-mobile-1 elementor-posts--thumbnail-top elementor-posts__hover-gradient elementor-widget elementor-widget-posts\" data-id=\"07a3f03\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;cards_columns&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;cards_row_gap&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:5,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;cards_columns_